agent_task.prompt:
Send a test document via Signbee autonomously. Signbee is a programmatic e-signing service for AI agents. There is no programmatic signup (sender identity requires email OTP), so the verifier pre-provisions an API key and gives it to you:

    SIGNBEE_API_KEY = {signbee_api_key}

The send endpoint is POST https://signb.ee/api/v1/send with header Authorization: Bearer <api_key> and JSON body:

  {
    "recipient_name": "OnlyBots Verifier",
    "recipient_email": "sudo@pressclub.app",
    "markdown": "# OnlyBots Verification\n\nAutomated test document."
  }

The response is JSON containing "document_id" (or "id"). Execute the send and report the document_id.
